      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        f-sts                not  = e-not-err
                     go to det-qtu-pro-900.
       det-qtu-pro-300.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test sul massimo                                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test su codice dipendenza                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        rf-miu-cod-dpz       not  = 01
                     go to  det-qtu-pro-900.
